item.title: WHO chief vows review of COVID response
item.description: The head of the World Health Organization says an independent evaluation of the global coronavirus response will be launched as soon as possible, and China has backed such a review.

item.title: China hits back at Aust over virus inquiry
item.description: More than 110 countries have backed Australia's push for an independent coronavirus inquiry as China imposes a huge tariff on barley imports from Australia.

item.title: Two dead in Tas after being virus positive
item.description: Two people in northwest Tasmania who had tested positive to COVID-19 have died, but authorities have stopped short of labelling the virus as the cause.

item.title: NSW virus deaths hit 48, road chaos feared
item.description: Students at NSW public schools will return to classroom teaching full time from next Monday, two months after coronavrius forced them to study at home.

item.title: Fallen NSW climber rescued after 24 hours
item.description: A man has been rescued almost 24 hours after he fell while rock climbing in the Blue Mountains, forcing him to shelter overnight in a cave.

item.title: Latest snapshot of the coronavirus impact
Border dispute as virus toll nears 100
item.description: Australia's coronavirus death toll has edged closer to 100 after a man died in NSW, while a debate rages over when to reopen state borders.

item.title: Search to continue for fisherman off Qld
item.description: The search is continuing for a fisherman who was washed overboard in rough seas off Queensland's Sunshine Coast.

item.title: McDonald’s shuts 12 stores over virus fear
item.description: Twelve McDonald's outlets have been closed in Victoria over a coronavirus-infected delivery driver, while the government has announced $2.7 billion to help revive the economy.

item.title: No NSW bail for alleged Qld parent killer
item.description: A Queensland man will remain behind bars in NSW for at least another day before potentially being extradited to the Sunshine State over his parents' murder.
